{"tid":1809631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登究竟有其多人對現行政制有認識，成日唔清楚就屌屌屌","createTime":"2020-01-03T08:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T03:14:12.000Z","uid":134794,"like":88,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"58e7f94b553716d121ef2487922c61625e48103b","tid":1809631,"uid":134794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809163\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809163</a><br />\n<br />\n美國人權法話到明要今年取消功能組別，點解仲有人高調唱反調？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809163</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n要取消功能組別就要修改基本法<br />\n修改基本法其中一關就係要全體立法會議員2/3支持<br />\n你唔拎功能組別<br />\n點修改基本法？！<br />\n等中共良心發現定美帝派兵？<br />\n就算美帝撐我地取消功能組別<br />\n都會係跟基本法<br />\n因為美國到目前為止都係承認基本法同一國兩制<br />\n除非你認為美國會為左香港派兵<br />\n咁已經係另一回事"},{"pid":"178541a4ad8dc85d08400a25616bf184e19af967","tid":1809631,"uid":195827,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"可以由行政長官提出議案<br />\n由該立法會組別一半或以上<br />\n或者全體立法會過半<br />\n就可以通過<br />\n<br />\n政制改革一般肯定係上大會投票<br />\n<br />\n所以取消功能組別 雙普選 不可或缺"},{"pid":"58f3c10317916e5db3a77e625320c0a38f1727d8","tid":1809631,"uid":146030,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:58:30.000Z","msg":"改附件二要經人大㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4ffa7821d1ef33d2f28a85b40dcb00d36b9e03","tid":1809631,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a804dff6bd5e2b10019a3179438e84508f236c9a","tid":1809631,"uid":51183,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:02:32.000Z","msg":"新九組模式<br />\n根本功能組別廢唔廢都無所謂"},{"pid":"e9fdbdf29717267136714b472db0fd00cb0a49ae","tid":1809631,"uid":134794,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"58f3c10317916e5db3a77e625320c0a38f1727d8","tid":1809631,"uid":14603